  "detailed_description": "<h1>Feature List</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533680/extras/d478dbe9a88715ee0aee56127a34d9e7.avif?t=1774036468\" width=880 height=256 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533680/extras/4e4f8ef7d905aace0b9220afbf5d84eb.poster.avif?t=1774036468\" width=880 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533680/extras/4e4f8ef7d905aace0b9220afbf5d84eb.webm?t=1774036468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533680/extras/4e4f8ef7d905aace0b9220afbf5d84eb.mp4?t=1774036468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533680/extras/1606890130eee1f83be33cccbb1e6c8f.poster.avif?t=1774036468\" width=880 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533680/extras/1606890130eee1f83be33cccbb1e6c8f.webm?t=1774036468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533680/extras/1606890130eee1f83be33cccbb1e6c8f.mp4?t=1774036468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533680/extras/e6ad78d04b2565fdcea0be250cdfeacd.poster.avif?t=1774036468\" width=880 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533680/extras/e6ad78d04b2565fdcea0be250cdfeacd.webm?t=1774036468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533680/extras/e6ad78d04b2565fdcea0be250cdfeacd.mp4?t=1774036468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recruit a squad of elite mercenaries, experts in post-apocalyptic zombie combat. Battle hordes of the dead as you explore a 3D world revealed through the cards.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533680/extras/ca7b0710d41815761c7190c76103a1f5.avif?t=1774036468\" width=616 height=64 /></span> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >» Go silent and keep the noise down, picking off enemies one by one.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >» Go loud with guns and explosives, drawing the dead at a rapid pace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >» Set them on fire or blow them up. Slice and dice your orchestrated zombie funeral.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533680/extras/a58dadf32201560924610e32cf1b4f26.avif?t=1774036468\" width=616 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >» 15 mercenary characters, each individually voiced with different personalities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >» 5 classes with 115 unique skills and special passive perks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > » Unlimited skill respec for endless experimentation. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >» Reanimate the dead to  transform into a special class, called Revenant.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >» 17 character specific attributes to fine-tune the combat style even further. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >» 350 Steam achievements, view progression directly in the game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >» 5 challenge modes with Leaderboards to replay the game with alternative rules.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533680/extras/f6d736d466278a373379379a51f22e77.avif?t=1774036468\" width=616 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >» Find and upgrade hundreds of weapons, consumables and gadgets for your squad.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >» Over 100 unique items that enhance your skills and transform your playstyle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >» Meet survivors to join your camp, where they’ll assist you in future missions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >» Complete 42 side missions with bonus rewards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533680/extras/f1ff903f6b136b66555944cabb6075d0.webp?t=1774036468\" width=616 height=48 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533680/extras/4e4f8ef7d905aace0b9220afbf5d84eb.poster.avif?t=1774036468\" width=880 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533680/extras/4e4f8ef7d905aace0b9220afbf5d84eb.webm?t=1774036468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533680/extras/4e4f8ef7d905aace0b9220afbf5d84eb.mp4?t=1774036468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533680/extras/1606890130eee1f83be33cccbb1e6c8f.poster.avif?t=1774036468\" width=880 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533680/extras/1606890130eee1f83be33cccbb1e6c8f.webm?t=1774036468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533680/extras/1606890130eee1f83be33cccbb1e6c8f.mp4?t=1774036468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533680/extras/e6ad78d04b2565fdcea0be250cdfeacd.poster.avif?t=1774036468\" width=880 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533680/extras/e6ad78d04b2565fdcea0be250cdfeacd.webm?t=1774036468\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533680/extras/e6ad78d04b2565fdcea0be250cdfeacd.mp4?t=1774036468\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Recruit a squad of elite mercenaries, experts in post-apocalyptic zombie combat. Battle hordes of the dead as you explore a 3D world revealed through the cards.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533680/extras/ca7b0710d41815761c7190c76103a1f5.avif?t=1774036468\" width=616 height=64 /></span> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >» Go silent and keep the noise down, picking off enemies one by one.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >» Go loud with guns and explosives, drawing the dead at a rapid pace.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >» Set them on fire or blow them up. Slice and dice your orchestrated zombie funeral.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533680/extras/a58dadf32201560924610e32cf1b4f26.avif?t=1774036468\" width=616 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >» 15 mercenary characters, each individually voiced with different personalities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >» 5 classes with 115 unique skills and special passive perks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > » Unlimited skill respec for endless experimentation. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >» Reanimate the dead to  transform into a special class, called Revenant.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >» 17 character specific attributes to fine-tune the combat style even further. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >» 350 Steam achievements, view progression directly in the game. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >» 5 challenge modes with Leaderboards to replay the game with alternative rules.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533680/extras/f6d736d466278a373379379a51f22e77.avif?t=1774036468\" width=616 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >» Find and upgrade hundreds of weapons, consumables and gadgets for your squad.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >» Over 100 unique items that enhance your skills and transform your playstyle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >» Meet survivors to join your camp, where they’ll assist you in future missions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >» Complete 42 side missions with bonus rewards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1533680/extras/f1ff903f6b136b66555944cabb6075d0.webp?t=1774036468\" width=616 height=48 /></span></p>",
